    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>1.Login with problem_user / secret_sauce<br/>
2.Click the "Name (A to Z)" dropdown menu<br/>
3.Select "Price (low to high)"</p>

<p>Expected: Products are sorted by price (ascending)</p>

<p>Actual: The order does not change, or the same products are displayed in random order</p>

<p>Severity: Major (prevents functionality)</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

