    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>1. Log in as problem_user<br/>
2.For the "Sauce Labs Bolt T-Shirt" product, click "Add to cart"</p>

<p>Expected: The button changes to "Remove"</p>

<p>Actual: It remains "Add to cart" (but the product is added-verified in the cart)</p>

<p>Severity: Medium (visual bug, but the functionality works)</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
