    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>1.Log in as standard_user<br/>
2.Log out from the menu (burger menu → Log out)</p>

<p>Expected: The fields are empty</p>

<p>Actual: The username "standard_user" remains visible; the password remains hidden but has not been cleared (can be seen using the inspector)</p>

<p>Severity: Low (potential security risk)</p>
            <br/>
